## 📦 PROJECT SNAPSHOT

**MeatvoApp** — Single-store meat delivery, 5km radius, India
- Store location: one dark store
- Delivery: within 5km, target <30 min
- Currency: ₹ (INR) always
- OTP: MSG91, **4-DIGIT** (NOT 6-digit — this is already built)

### What EXISTS (do NOT rebuild):
```
backend/         → ~50% built, Node.js + Express
                   - MSG91 OTP (4-digit) ✅ working
                   - Some routes exist — SCAN before adding
admin/           → HTML/CSS/JS webapp — fully built UI
                   - Needs real API connection (replaces mock data)
customer webapp  → HTML/CSS/JS — OLD, being replaced by Flutter
delivery webapp  → HTML/CSS/JS — OLD, being replaced by Flutter
```

### What NEEDS BUILDING:
```
backend/         → Complete remaining 50%: orders, payment, websocket, partner assignment
customer-app/    → Flutter app (fresh build) — connect to backend API
delivery-app/    → Flutter app (fresh build) — connect to backend API
admin/js/        → Replace fetch() mock calls with real API endpoints
```

