## 🏗️ TECH STACK (locked — do not change without updating ARCHITECTURE.md)

### Backend
- Runtime: Node.js + TypeScript
- Framework: Express.js
- ORM: Prisma + PostgreSQL
- Auth: JWT (access 15min, refresh 7d) + MSG91 OTP (4-digit)
- Real-time: ws (WebSocket)
- Validation: Zod
- Queue: Bull + Redis (notifications, retries)

### Flutter (both apps)
- State: Riverpod
- HTTP: Dio with interceptors (JWT auto-attach)
- Storage: flutter_secure_storage (tokens), shared_preferences (settings)
- Maps: google_maps_flutter
- Navigation: GoRouter
- Push: firebase_messaging (FCM)

### Admin (HTML/JS — keep as-is, just connect)
- HTTP: native fetch() with auth wrapper
- Real-time: native WebSocket
- Charts: Chart.js
- Maps: Leaflet.js

---

## 🔐 RBAC — 3 Roles (strict, never mix)
```
ADMIN            → full access, admin panel only
CUSTOMER         → place orders, track, manage addresses
DELIVERY_PARTNER → accept/reject orders, update status, GPS ping
```
Every protected route MUST check: authenticate → then checkRole

---

## 🚦 ORDER STATUS FLOW (NEVER skip steps)
```
PENDING → CONFIRMED → PACKED → OUT_FOR_DELIVERY → DELIVERED
                   ↘ CANCELLED (only from PENDING or CONFIRMED)
```

---

## 🇮🇳 INDIA-SPECIFIC RULES
- Phone: 10-digit, regex `/^[6-9]\d{9}$/`
- OTP: **4-digit** (MSG91, already integrated)
- Payment: PhonePe UPI primary, COD mandatory
- Price: always ₹, never $
- Date: DD/MM/YYYY, Time: 12-hour IST
- Delivery radius: 5km from store

---

## ⚡ WEBSOCKET EVENTS
```javascript
// Server → Client
"order:new"               → admin gets new order alert
"order:status_update"     → { orderId, status, timestamp }
"order:partner_assigned"  → { orderId, partner: { name, phone, lat, lng } }
"partner:location_update" → { orderId, lat, lng }

// Client → Server  
"partner:location"        → { lat, lng }  // every 5 seconds when on delivery
"partner:online"          → { partnerId }
"partner:offline"         → { partnerId }
```

---

## 🤖 PARTNER ASSIGNMENT ALGORITHM
```
Score = (1/distance_km × 40) + (acceptanceRate × 30) + (rating × 20) + (todayBonus × 10)
- Only partners within 5km AND online AND no active delivery
- 30-second accept window → auto-reassign to next
- Max 3 reassignment attempts → admin alert
```

---

## 🛡️ SECURITY CHECKLIST (check before every PR)
- [ ] No hardcoded secrets (use process.env always)
- [ ] Auth middleware on every protected route
- [ ] Role check AFTER auth check
- [ ] Zod validation on ALL inputs
- [ ] PhonePe webhook: SHA256 signature verified
- [ ] OTP: max 3 attempts per phone per 10 min (Redis rate limit)
- [ ] Stock: atomic decrement (PostgreSQL transaction)
- [ ] Payment: idempotency key on every payment create

